{"tha-ap404:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap404:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap404:0.3":"Punnakattheraapadana ","tha-ap404:1.1":"“Pabbharakutam nissaya, ","tha-ap404:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap404:1.3":"Abadhiko ca so buddho, ","tha-ap404:1.4":"vasati pabbatantare. ","tha-ap404:2.1":"Mama assamasamanta, ","tha-ap404:2.2":"panado asi tavade; ","tha-ap404:2.3":"Buddhe nibbayamanamhi, ","tha-ap404:2.4":"aloko udapajjatha. ","tha-ap404:3.1":"Yavata vanasandasmim, ","tha-ap404:3.2":"acchakokataracchaka; ","tha-ap404:3.3":"Vala ca kesari sabbe, ","tha-ap404:3.4":"abhigajjimsu tavade. ","tha-ap404:4.1":"Uppatam tamaham disva, ","tha-ap404:4.2":"pabbharam agamasaham; ","tha-ap404:4.3":"Tatthaddassasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap404:4.4":"nibbutam aparajitam. ","tha-ap404:5.1":"Suphullam salarajamva, ","tha-ap404:5.2":"sataramsimva uggatam; ","tha-ap404:5.3":"Vitaccikamva angaram, ","tha-ap404:5.4":"nibbutam aparajitam. ","tha-ap404:6.1":"Tinam katthanca puretva, ","tha-ap404:6.2":"citakam tatthakasaham; ","tha-ap404:6.3":"Citakam sukatam katva, ","tha-ap404:6.4":"sariram jhapayim aham. ","tha-ap404:7.1":"Sariram jhapayitvana, ","tha-ap404:7.2":"gandhatoyam samokirim; ","tha-ap404:7.3":"Antalikkhe thito yakkho, ","tha-ap404:7.4":"namamaggahi tavade. ","tha-ap404:8.1":"‘Yam puritam taya kiccam, ","tha-ap404:8.2":"sayambhussa mahesino; ","tha-ap404:8.3":"Punnako nama namena, ","tha-ap404:8.4":"sada hohi tuvam mune’. ","tha-ap404:9.1":"Tamha kaya cavitvana, ","tha-ap404:9.2":"devalokam agacchaham; ","tha-ap404:9.3":"Tattha dibbamayo gandho, ","tha-ap404:9.4":"antalikkha pavassati. ","tha-ap404:10.1":"Tatrapi namadheyyam me, ","tha-ap404:10.2":"punnakoti ahu tada; ","tha-ap404:10.3":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap404:10.4":"sankappam purayamaham. ","tha-ap404:11.1":"Idam pacchimakam mayham, ","tha-ap404:11.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap404:11.3":"Idhapi punnako nama, ","tha-ap404:11.4":"namadheyyam pakasati. ","tha-ap404:12.1":"Tosayitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap404:12.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap404:12.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap404:12.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap404:13.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap404:13.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap404:13.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap404:13.4":"tanukiccassidam phalam. ","tha-ap404:14.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap404:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap404:14.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap404:15.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap404:15.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap404:15.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap404:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap404:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap404:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap404:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma punnako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap404:18.1":"Punnakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}